The 81 Division, Nigerian Army has reacted to a viral video of a soldier fighting with a Policeman in Lagos State. A statement issued and signed by Lt.-Col. Olaniyi Osoba said the Army division has commenced an investigation into the incident. The video currently trending on social media shows a soldier engaged in a fierce fight with a policeman in Apongbon, Lagos Island on Wednesday. Osoba said the Division was looking into the matter to fully ascertain what transpired between both parties. He added that necessary sanctions will be taken after the investigation.